#

Mediterranean Toast

15 min
$5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianMediterraneanHealthy

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

AppetizerSnack

Tags:

QuickEasyToastHealthy

Description

A delightful and healthy toast topped with fresh Mediterranean flavors like tomatoes, olives, and feta cheese.

Ingredients

  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup
  • kalamata olives: 1/4 cup
  • fresh basil: 1/4 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
